RIVER_STAGE      00:00     7.60
RIVER_STAGE      00:50     7.80
RIVER_STAGE      01:10     8.10
RIVER_STAGE      01:40     8.55
RIVER_STAGE      02:10     8.30
RIVER_STAGE      03:00     7.80

[CONTROLS]
RULE PUMP_ON
IF NODE PUMP_WETWELL DEPTH > 0.80
THEN PUMP PUMP_STATION STATUS = ON

RULE PUMP_OFF
IF NODE PUMP_WETWELL DEPTH < 0.25
THEN PUMP PUMP_STATION STATUS = OFF

[REPORT]
INPUT      NO
CONTROLS   YES
SUBCATCHMENTS ALL
NODES ALL
LINKS ALL

[TAGS]

[MAP]
DIMENSIONS 0 0 1000 700
Units      Meters

